---

<section class="reviews">
  <div class="reviews__container">
    <div class="reviews__top">
      <p class="reviews__paragraph">
        Our track record speaks for itself. We've assisted countless partners,
        spanning from fledgling startups to thriving medium-sized enterprises,
        in reaching their objectives.
      </p>
      <div class="reviews__google">
        <Icon name="flat-color-icons:google" class="reviews__google--icon" />
        <p class="reviews__google--text">40+ Reviews</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="reviews__mid">
      <div class="reviews__title">
        <h1>Reviews From Our Customers</h1>
        <sapn class="reviews__title--icon-co">
          <Icon name="entypo:quote" class="reviews__title--icon" />
        </sapn>
      </div>

      <div class="reviews__buttons">
        <button class="reviews__prev">
          <Icon class="reviews__icon reviews__icon-1" name="ep:arrow-up-bold" />
          <Icon class="reviews__icon reviews__icon-1" name="ep:arrow-up-bold" />
        </button>
        <button class="reviews__next">
          <Icon class="reviews__icon reviews__icon-2" name="ep:arrow-up-bold" />
          <Icon class="reviews__icon reviews__icon-2" name="ep:arrow-up-bold" />
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="reviews-list reviews__slider swiper">
      <div class="swiper-wrapper reviews__wrapper">
        <!-- Reviw -->
        <figure class="review swiper-slide">
          <p class="review__text">
            "Fantastic results! They boosted our online presence and traffic.
            Highly recommended!"
          </p>
